                            <comment id="14653419" author="srowen" created="Tue, 4 Aug 2015 10:26:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This isn&apos;t quite right: the method that the shim loader is looking for was added in Hadoop 2.1, not 2.0. The CDH release is technically fine in this regard. I&apos;ll post more on the PR.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
